{"id":1498,"date":"2026-07-02T13:11:15","date_gmt":"2026-07-02T12:11:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/?page_id=1498"},"modified":"2026-07-08T01:21:16","modified_gmt":"2026-07-08T00:21:16","slug":"robatex-humanitarian-mine-detecting-robot","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/robatex-humanitarian-mine-detecting-robot\/","title":{"rendered":"RobaTex \u2013 Humanitarian Mine Detecting Robot"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1498\" class=\"elementor elementor-1498\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-156804c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"156804c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83e278e elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"83e278e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/robotic_projects\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">\u2190 Back to Robotics Projects<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66c6464 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"66c6464\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4953d4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a4953d4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">RobaTex - Humanitarian Mine Detecting Robot<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ccf353b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ccf353b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b1d91c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1b1d91c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd7d0af e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bd7d0af\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1f3bbc9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1f3bbc9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_side-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1729\" alt=\"robatex side\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_side-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_side-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_side-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_side.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"RobaTex \u2013 Humanitarian Mine Detecting Robot\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3803db8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3803db8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-627fdc0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"627fdc0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a30d1b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6a30d1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_front-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1728\" alt=\"robatex front\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_front-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_front-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_front-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Robatex_front.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"RobaTex \u2013 Humanitarian Mine Detecting Robot\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24a16a8 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"24a16a8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df551de elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"df551de\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Humanitarian demining is a dangerous and time-consuming process. The aim of RobaTex was to develop a low-cost robotic platform capable of remotely exploring hazardous environments while providing the operator with live video, environmental perception, and simulated mine detection.<\/p><p>The robot combines multiple Raspberry Pi computers, cameras, LiDAR, ROS, and a custom operator interface to create a modular robotic platform that can be remotely controlled while displaying real-time sensor information.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29f3f09 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"29f3f09\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f16059 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9f16059\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Project Information<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0216fef e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0216fef\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9b03829 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9b03829\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Duration<\/strong><br \/>2023 \u2013 2025<\/p><p><strong>Team<\/strong><br \/>3 students (later 2)<\/p><p><strong>Role<\/strong><br \/>Robotics Systems Integration &amp; Software Development<\/p><p><strong>Technologies<\/strong><\/p><p>Python \u2022 ROS1 \u2022 Raspberry Pi \u2022 OpenCV \u2022 LiDAR \u2022 TCP\/IP \u2022 Linux \u2022 Git \u2022 Fusion 360<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0f7844 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e0f7844\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">My Contributions<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f649dd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2f649dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Throughout the project, I worked on the integration of both the hardware and software components, ensuring that the different subsystems operated reliably together.<\/p><p><strong>Robotics Integration<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Integrated three Raspberry Pi computers into a distributed architecture.<\/li><li>Configured ROS and the embedded Linux environment.<\/li><li>Connected and configured cameras, LiDAR and networking.<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Software Development<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Developed Python programs for sensor acquisition and processing.<\/li><li>Integrated LiDAR data and computer vision pipelines.<\/li><li>Implemented automatic startup of the robot using Bash scripts and systemd.<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>System Validation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Integrated and tested all hardware components.<\/li><li>Debugged communication between subsystems.<\/li><li>Assisted with software recovery after the robot environment was accidentally reset.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b967bd elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1b967bd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">System Architecture<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7c297d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d7c297d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>To improve modularity and distribute the computational load, the robot was divided into three independent computing units.<\/p><ul><li>Raspberry Pi 4 \u2013 Robot control running ROS.<\/li><li>Raspberry Pi 5 \u2013 Camera acquisition, LiDAR processing and SLAM.<\/li><li>Raspberry Pi 4 \u2013 Touchscreen operator interface displaying live sensor data.<\/li><\/ul><p>This modular architecture simplified debugging, improved maintainability and allowed several software modules to run simultaneously.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e4e06b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e4e06b5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Features<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64f87ef elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"64f87ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Computer Vision<\/strong><\/p><p>The robot detects simulated mines using ArUco markers. Images are processed in real time before the detection results are transmitted to the operator interface.<\/p><p><strong>LiDAR Mapping<\/strong><\/p><p>An RPLidar A1 provides a 360\u00b0 scan of the environment. The acquired data is processed and visualised in real time to improve operator awareness and support SLAM experiments.<\/p><p><strong>Operator Interface<\/strong><\/p><p>A touchscreen interface was developed in Python, allowing the operator to monitor multiple live data streams simultaneously while remotely controlling the robot.<\/p><p>Displayed information included:<\/p><ul><li>Navigation camera<\/li><li>Mine detection camera<\/li><li>LiDAR visualisation<\/li><li>SLAM output<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5687dcb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5687dcb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engineering Challenges<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dd40d47 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dd40d47\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>One of the biggest challenges was integrating multiple hardware and software components into a reliable system.<\/p><p>Several improvements were implemented throughout development, including:<\/p><ul><li>Automatic startup of ROS services after boot.<\/li><li>Recovery and reconstruction of the robot software after a complete system reset.<\/li><li>Debugging communication between multiple Raspberry Pi computers.<\/li><li>Integration of several simultaneous sensor streams while maintaining system stability.<\/li><\/ul><p>Although the SLAM algorithm successfully generated maps, localisation remained unreliable due to odometry and synchronisation limitations. This highlighted the importance of robust localisation and provided valuable insight into the challenges of autonomous robotics.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-89156d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"89156d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Results<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3719c1d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3719c1d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The final prototype successfully demonstrated:<\/p><p>\u2714 Remote robot operation<\/p><p>\u2714 Live camera streaming<\/p><p>\u2714 ArUco marker detection<\/p><p>\u2714 Real-time LiDAR visualisation<\/p><p>\u2714 Modular multi-computer architecture<\/p><p>\u2714 Touchscreen operator interface<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e94b6d9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e94b6d9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What I Learned<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-39db82e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"39db82e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This project strengthened my understanding of robotics as a multidisciplinary engineering field where successful integration is just as important as individual software or mechanical components.<\/p><p>Beyond developing software, I gained practical experience in ROS, embedded Linux, computer vision, networking, sensor integration, and debugging complex robotic systems. Most importantly, I learned how careful system architecture and modular design significantly improve the reliability and maintainability of large robotics projects.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u2190 Back to Robotics Projects RobaTex &#8211; Humanitarian Mine Detecting Robot Humanitarian demining is a dangerous and time-consuming process. The aim of RobaTex was to develop a low-cost robotic platform capable of remotely exploring hazardous environments while providing the operator with live video, environmental perception, and simulated mine detection. The robot combines multiple Raspberry Pi [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"disabled","footer-sml-layout":"","ast-disable-related-posts":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"default","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"